{
  "stem": "19211.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they hired him to work there as an accountant.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even-- no, that's-- the Russians did that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- the Russians occupied us from 1939 till 1941.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Russians--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to do, to do the work for them, yes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was an accountant there, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to-- remember, I went to school there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went to the general public school there, which was quite a change from where-- I was not used to it-- from where I was before.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember I finished seven grades before the war started, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, there, there was mixed-- it was a mixed class.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were other Jews, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was not used to being mixed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to parochial school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was mixed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we didn't have any problems.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything was just going smooth this way.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The courses were taught in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we had some Russian we were forced to take.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But mostly it was in Polish, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we continued with our physics and our math and all the courses we took before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- it was a little-- you know, a adjustment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't too bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I adjusted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Right now, I barely speak English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I used to speak four or five different languages before.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I have not--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's correct, Yiddish, Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to speak fluent Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Ukrainian, Russian I used to speak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when I moved to Germany, I had learned German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to learn German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I spoke a little German, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, we were in Brody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, suddenly, in 1941-- I think it was June or July-- we heard, like, explosions.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the Germans [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] came to occupy.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
